<div class='documentTop'><div>
  
  
    <h1>The Norwegian follow-up of OSCE’s Election Assessment Mission report</h1>
  
  </div></div>
  

  <div class="documentBody" id="Tekstinnhold">   
  <div>
    <p>At the invitation of the Norwegian Government OSCE (The Organization for Security and Co-operation in Europe) deployed an Election Assessment Mission during the General Election in September 2009. The Election Assessment Mission was carried out by the OSCE’s office for Democratic Institutions and Human Rights (ODHIR). This resulted in an Election Assessment Mission Report that was presented 27 November 2009. </p>
<p><a href="/upload/KRD/Kampanjer/valgportal/valgobservatorer/Report_Follow_Up_EAM_Norway_2010_ENGLISH_FINAL.PDF"><img class="floatRight" alt="Picture of the report. Click to get to the report" src="/upload/KRD/Kampanjer/valgportal/valgobservatorer/Forside_rapport_response_180.jpg" /></a>In a response to this EAM report, the Ministry of Local Government and Regional Development presented a report to OSCE/ODHIR 31 May 2010. The response report gives an overview of the requests contained in the OSCE report and the Ministry’s planned follow-up of these requests.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>
<p>The Ministry has, in cooperation with the Permanent Delegation of Norway to the OSCE, also presented the response report for the OSCE Human Dimension Committee and the Permanent Council in Vienna. </p>
<p>By doing this, Norway is contributing to establishing a new practise for the follow-up of election observations and election assessment reports from OSCE.&nbsp; </p>
<p>Relevant links for more information (all documents in pdf-format):</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/upload/KRD/Kampanjer/valgportal/valgobservatorer/Report_Follow_Up_EAM_Norway_2010_ENGLISH_FINAL.PDF">Response report to OSCE’s EAM report of 27 November 2009 Norway, 31 May 2010</a></li>
<li><a href="/upload/KRD/Kampanjer/valgportal/valgobservatorer/Vik_HumanDimensionCommittee.pdf">Introduction held by Ambassador Guttorm Vik at the Human Dimension Committee meeting in Vienna 8 June 2010</a> </li>
<li><a href="/upload/KRD/Kampanjer/valgportal/valgobservatorer/Riise_HumanDimensionCommitee.pdf">Presentation held by Professional Director Marianne Riise from the Ministry of Local Government and Regional Development at the Human Dimension Committee meeting in Vienna 8 June 2010</a> </li>
<li><a href="/upload/KRD/Kampanjer/valgportal/valgobservatorer/Vik_Permanent_Council.pdf">Presentation held by Ambassador Guttorm Vik at the OSCE Permanent Council meeting 10 June 2010</a></li>
<li><a href="/upload/KRD/Kampanjer/valgportal/valgobservatorer/Bronebakk_HumanDimensionCommittee.pdf">Presentation held by ambassador Jørg Willy Bronebakk at the 20th Anniversary Conference for the Copenhagen-document</a><br /><br /></li>
<li>The OSCE’s EAM report, 27 November 2009<br />[<a href="/upload/KRD/Kampanjer/valgportal/valgobservatorer/OSSE-rapport_ved_stortingsvalget_2009.pdf">In Norwegian</a>]&nbsp; [<a href="http://www.osce.org/documents/odihr/2009/11/41624_en.pdf">In English</a>] </li></ul>
  </div>
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
  
